<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="ko">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>EMA514_01_IH_0001_s</title>

    <!-- 공통 js-->
    <script src="../../common_contents/common/js/app.js"></script>
    <script src="../../common_practice/common/js/solve_area_act.js"></script>

    <!-- 공통 css-->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_contents/common/css/app.css" />

    <!-- 개별 -->
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/common/css/app.css" />
    <link rel="stylesheet" href="./../../common_practice/css/ema514_01.css" />
  </head>
  <body>
    <div id="app_wrap" class="ema514_01_ih_0001">
      <section class="title type2 flex_wrap">
        <h2 lang="y">
          <span class="recap" lang="y">이전에 <span>배웠어요</span></span>
        </h2>
        <div class="title_sub">
          <span lang="y">『수학 3-1』 분수를 소수로, 소수를 분수로 나타내기</span>
        </div>
      </section>
      <section class="title type2">
        <h2 data-head="1" lang="y"><span class="empty_box nemo head"></span>안에 알맞은 분수 또는 소수를 써넣으세요.</h2>
      </section>

      <section class="contents">
        <div class="question_box">
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">0</div>
            <div class="bottom">0</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>1</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.1</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(2)/(10)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.2</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>3</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.3</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>4</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.4</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>5</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="0.5"></math-field></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>6</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.6</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="input_wrap fraction_wrap">
                <math-field data-answer-single="(7)/(10)" text-align="center"></math-field>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.7</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>8</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">0.8</div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">
              <div class="fraction_box">
                <span>9</span>
                <span>10</span>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bottom">
              <div class="input_wrap"><math-field data-answer-single="0.9"></math-field></div>
            </div>
          </div>
          <div class="item">
            <div class="top">1</div>
            <div class="bottom">1</div>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="solve_area">
          <div class="inner_solve">
            <div class="flex">
              <strong class="tit_solve" lang="y">해설</strong>
              <div class="conts_solve">
                <p lang="y">분모가 10인 분수는 소수 한 자리 수로 나타낼 수 있고, 소수 한 자리 수는 분모가 10인 분수로 나타낼 수 있습니다.</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="buttons_solve"></div>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="btn_area">
          <button class="btnType key">입력타입토글</button>
          <button class="btnReset">리셋</button>
          <button class="btnCheck">확인</button>
        </div>
      </section>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
